---
title: Secret Retrieval - Deploy Time vs Boot Time
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph DEPLOY_TIME["❌ Deploy Time (CF ValueFrom)"]
        CF["CloudFormation"] -->|"resolves secret"| SM1["Secrets Manager"]
        CF -->|"injects value into"| UD1["UserData / Metadata"]
        UD1 -->|"secret VISIBLE in stack"| EC2_A["EC2 boots with embedded secret"]
    end

    subgraph BOOT_TIME["✅ Boot Time (Instance Role + API)"]
        EC2_B["EC2 boots"] -->|"assumes IAM role"| ROLE["Instance Profile Role"]
        ROLE -->|"ssm:GetParameters at startup"| SSM["Parameter Store / Secrets Manager"]
        SSM -->|"returns secret to memory only"| EC2_B
    end

    style DEPLOY_TIME fill:#ffcccc,stroke:#cc0000
    style BOOT_TIME fill:#ccffcc,stroke:#00cc00
